{"tid":1220630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位義士 緊張時間睇J圖輕鬆下 越南妹尺度超開！ 熱褲三角洲全露","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T04:51:41.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a097404b5922d6e65cc9c0f5a86affca403d5f25","tid":1220630,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-06-13/900/20190613003511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-06-13%2F900%2F20190613003511.jpg&h=07ecd9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現代女性越來越敢穿，不吝嗇展現自己的好身材，有些衣服太前衛，常會讓網友認為「越來越不懂時尚」，畢竟「走的太前面」不是每個人都可以接受，這位正妹穿的短褲，最近就在網路上引起熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n越南的正妹不論是外表還是穿著，都越來越敢穿，大方秀性感，像這位在越南街頭的辣妹，穿著一件低腰牛仔熱褲，露出小蠻腰，乍看之下好像沒什麼，但仔細看一邊的褲子挖了一個大洞，破洞大到幾乎露出下面三角洲，不論任何角度看起來都會曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-06-13/900/20190613003520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-06-13%2F900%2F20190613003520.jpg&h=f2cbe5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n褲子破到三角洲若隱若現(圖片取自/爆笑三叔微博)<br />\n<br />\n尤其其中一張照片是騎上腳踏車，神祕三角洲更是一覽無遺，這件褲子設計太新潮又大膽，讓許多偏保守的越南網友看不下去，在網路上罵聲不斷，質疑這位正妹要這樣穿不如都不要穿，不停酸說「不怕冷風吹進洞嗎」、「是不是想引人犯罪」、「褲子自己剪的嗎」、「騎車這樣穿比較涼嗎」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXYVdEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXYVdEY.jpg&h=dbe19ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNoqATj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNoqATj.jpg&h=b79b1735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LZ5ATk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LZ5ATk.jpg&h=85694d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWOx0j0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWOx0j0.jpg&h=0823b351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hXsrkj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhXsrkj0.jpg&h=29aede2d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}